high_descs: turn right and head across the room to the counter with the sink on the right
turn and face the counter to pick up the knife with the yellow handle that is behind the spoon
turn to the left to face the white table with the loaf of bread
slice the loaf of bread that is on the table
turn back to the right to face the counter again
, open the drawer on the left side of the sink and place the knife inside the drawer to the right of the two forks with the pointed edge facing forward
turn back to the left facing the table with the loaf of bread
pick up a slice of bread
turn and walk to the other side of the room passing the dining table on your right to the microwave in the corner to the right of the silver trash can
open the microwave door, place the slice of bread into the microwave, close the door, cook for five seconds and remove the bread from the microwave
turn around and go back across the room turning right to face the counter
place the slice of bread on the counter in front of the spoon and to the right of the tomato
anns.task_desc: put a cooked slice of bread on to the counter

high_descs: Walk past the refrigerator and the sink to the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife.
Turn left and walk to the counter with the loaf of bread on it.
Slice the loaf with the knife.
Walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Open the left door, put the knife in it, and close it.
Turn left to the counter with the bread on it.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around and walk to the microwave in the corner of the room.
Place the bread in the microwave, heat it, and take it out.
Walk back to the counter to the left of the sink.
Place the bread down on the counter in front of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated slice of bread on a counter.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room and turn right to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and face the bread on the table.
Cut the bread on the table into slices.
Turn to the right to face the drawer at the end of the counter.
Place the knife in the drawer on the left end of the sink.
Turn left and step forward to face the bread on the table.
Pick up a slice of bread on the counter.
Turn around and walk across the room to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the bread slice and remove it from the microwave.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Place the bread slice on the counter beside the tomato.
anns.task_desc: To heat a bread slice and set it on the counter to the left of the stove.

high_descs: Turn left, go towards the trash can; turn right, go towards the far wall and turn right at the sink counter.
Pick up knife at the sink counter.
Turn around and make a right towards the table with the bread.
Use the knife to slice the bread on the table.
Turn around and head back towards the sink counter.
Open the sink counter drawer and place the knife in it.
Turn around and head back to the table with the bread.
Pick up a slice of bread.
Turn around, head towards the trash can and make a right then a left at the microwave oven sitting on a table.
Place the bread in the microwave and heat it.
Take the bread out, turn around and head back to the sink counter.
Place the slice of bread on the sink counter next to the spoon.
Move left until you are at the counter on the left side of the sink.
Pick up the long knife near the back of the counter
Turn to the left and go to the white table by the stove.
Slice the brown bread near the front of the table.
Turn back to the counter by the left side of the sink.
Go to the small drawer under the counter.  Open it.
Put the knife in the drawer.
Go back to the counter the sliced the bread is on the table.
Take a slice of bread and turn around and walk to the microwave.  Place the slice of bread in the microwave.
Warm the bread in the microwave.  When the microwave signals, remove the bread.
Close the microwave door, and take the bread to the counter on the left of the sink.
Put the slice of bread on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Slice a piece of bread & warm it up.  Leave it on the counter.

high_descs: Walk across the room to the counter by the sink.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and go to the table with a loaf of bread.
Slice the loaf of bread on the table.
Turn right and go back by the sink.
Open the drawer and put the knife in the drawer.
Turn left back to the loaf of bread.
Pick up a slice of bread from the loaf.
Turn around and walk across the room to the microwave.
Put the slice of bread in the microwave and heat it.
Turn around and walk across the room, then turn left to go to the counter by the sink.
Set the slice of bread down on the counter beside the tomato and in front of the spoon.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of bread on the counter.
